307
00:16:45,477 --> 00:16:50,989
Because she was doing my hair all the while from 20:00 to 21:00!

308
00:16:52,991 --> 00:16:54,993
Are you sure she was with you, right through?

309
00:16:54,993 --> 00:16:57,677
