00:17:14,177 --> 00:17:15,877
then carry him over here!

317
00:17:15,877 --> 00:17:18,077
But...

318
00:17:18,077 --> 00:17:20,077
But what?

319
00:17:24,077 --> 00:17:28,077
Oh no. Mom and dad are glaring at each other again.

320
00:17:30,277 --> 00:17:34,577
But, if what Eri said a while ago is true...

321
00:17:35,033 --> 00:17:39,877
Would you like to come to my shop?

322
00:17:48,077 --> 00:17:50,677
I guess this kind of thing off and on is not bad.

323
00:17:53,777 --> 00:17:56,077
Turn left at that intersection over there.

324
00:17:59,577 --> 00:18:01,477
Hey, just what do you think you're doing?

325
00:18:01,477 --> 00:18:03,061
When making a turn at the intersection,

326
00:18:03,061 --> 00:18:05,077
