327
00:18:05,077 --> 00:18:07,077
Keep to the traffic rules, will you?

328
00:18:07,077 --> 00:18:10,477
Oh boy. Then, why ride with me?

329
00:18:11,477 --> 00:18:13,071
That's my shop over there.

330
00:18:13,071 --> 00:18:14,377
What?

331
00:18:20,577 --> 00:18:21,877
Conan!

332
00:18:22,477 --> 00:18:25,083
What a terrible driving!

333
00:18:25,083 --> 00:18:27,877
It would've been better to walk here than take the car!

334
00:18:29,377 --> 00:18:32,477
-Are you all right? -Yep.

335
00:18:32,477 --> 00:18:34,077
I see.

336
00:18:34,077 --> 00:18:36,577
Ms. Kisaki, you were sitting here,

337
00:18:36,577 --> 00:18:39,577
