355
00:19:21,139 --> 00:19:22,877
So, I kept glancing at the clock.

356
00:19:22,877 --> 00:19:27,145
And? When and where did you go off to attend to your matters?

357
00:19:27,377 --> 00:19:28,677
During the waiting time for the color

358
00:19:28,677 --> 00:19:31,177
to set into my hair after she dyed it.

359
00:19:31,177 --> 00:19:34,377
If I remember correctly, I think it was

360
00:19:34,377 --> 00:19:36,577
for 10 minutes between 20:20 to 20:30.

